'''Drayson''' was a name shared by the following individuals:
*'''[[Drayson]]''', [[Nautolan/Legends|Nautolan]] [[Republic Military/Legends|Republic Military]] [[Commander/Legends|commander]] during the [[Korriban Incursion]] in the [[Galactic War]] with the [[Sith Empire (Post–Great Hyperspace War)|Sith Empire]]
*'''[[Drayson (Rebel)]]''', [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Alliance]] [[Commanding officer/Legends|commanding officer]] of [[Edan Base]] on [[Edan II/Legends|Edan II]]
*'''[[Hiram Drayson/Legends|Hiram Drayson]]''', Alliance and [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] [[Admiral/Legends|admiral]] and [[Director/Legends|director]] of [[Alpha Blue]]
*'''[[Bhindi Drayson]]''', daughter of Hiram Drayson and member, and eventual leader, of [[Wraith Squadron]]
